\id JAS - Abureni
\h A̠zemsi̠
\toc3 A̠zem
\toc2 A̠zemsi̠
\toc1 A̠d̠ire Ta̠ A̠zemsi̠
\mt2 A̠d̠ire Ta̠
\mt1 A̠zemsi̠
\imt1 Otighom
\ip O̠ni̠ wa̠ age̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ire onon bho̠ bha̠ A̠zemsi, umor onin onweni ta̠ A̠zizo̠s na̠ odi o̠ni̠ irileghom d̠a̠ Aso̠si̠ wa̠ d̠a̠ A̠zeruse̠le̠m bho̠. I̠na age̠ agi̠o̠m i̠pu̠r ogbo A̠zu ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st ya̠ na̠ e̠ro̠ d̠a̠ re̠ma ya̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zu bho̠, sekina̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st kesikesi bho̠. Ezin a̠d̠ire onon, bha̠ oselegi ima̠ra̠ igunugha̠, ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ima̠ra̠ ologi, ya̠a̠ a̠ma̠rugh d̠o̠yo̠ ko onwegia̠n d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ orugh a̠ma̠rugh ta̠ Akrai̠st. A̠d̠ire onon amara a̠wia̠n amu̠gho̠nyan wa̠ u̠gba ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ma̠ o̠da Akrai̠st obhin ma̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ ologhom i̠ki̠kara a̠ga̠i i̠di̠ar e̠mu̠gh, sa̠ ko o̠bi̠gh d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ga̠i a̠nwegia̠n d̠a̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar na̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an. A̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ikperekper a̠sidogh ya̠ ib̠uiy sa̠ i̠gu̠b̠an atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ta̠ Azizo̠s ya̠ i̠na aro̠ d̠a̠ anyu̠ igu atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠. A̠zemsi agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar ya̠ ado̠l a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ e̠da ma̠ Akrai̠st ebhin ta̠ e̠gu̠b̠an a̠ma̠rugh ima̠ra̠ ologi d̠a̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m Akrai̠st. I̠na agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ifa̠ga̠, okpon o̠ni̠ o̠do̠ti̠me̠ni̠, oguru, asi̠matan, ipoiny, o̠kpo̠ e̠mara̠nwunom, na̠ i̠gho̠r. A̠zemsi a̠bhin a̠d̠izo re̠kal a̠leriom agu̠o̠ a̠ga̠i ima̠ra̠ ologi ta̠ a̠mutiom ib̠eb̠i rogir. Opa̠n agu̠o̠ o̠gba bha̠, a̠ga̠i ima̠ra̠ ologi ta̠ amar ib̠eb̠i ogir a̠mutiom. I̠na agba ma̠a̠, ofugh ima̠ra̠ ologi d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ ku̠ku̠m na̠ olei d̠o̠, ma̠a̠ i̠yar ta̠ orugh o̠gu̠b̠e̠ni̠ (2:14). Elilegima̠ ta̠ a̠ga̠i ima̠ra̠ ologi d̠i̠yar bha̠ od̠i ka̠ a̠ghud̠um na̠ a̠nwegia̠n. I̠na a̠bhin ogbo ya̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ atu̠o̠m agu̠o̠ iriren na̠ emum itu ya̠ i̠gu̠b̠an awa bho̠. D̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ a̠d̠ire bho̠ amar agba a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i ogir bho̠, amar a̠bhon obhin o̠tu̠ghan ogboloma̠ a̠ma̠rugh ta̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st. Sene ma̠ a̠d̠ire ta̠ A̠zemsi ma̠ aro̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ amu̠gho̠n ikpo a̠fugh bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠gir nyen (1:22-25).
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠
\io1 A̠ga̠i a̠ghud̠um ima̠ra̠ ologi \ior (1:1-27)\ior*
\io1 A̠ma̠rugh na̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ ewia̠n ima̠ra̠ ologi \ior (2:1-13)\ior*
\io1 Ima̠ra̠ ologi na̠ ogir \ior (2:14-26)\ior*
\io1 Agu̠o̠ obhin okpoghoriom a̠nem bho̠ \ior (3:1-18)\ior*
\io1 Ib̠eb̠i a̠kikiom \ior (4:11-17)\ior*
\io1 U̠ghaghana ma̠ o̠li̠la bho̠ \ior (5:1-6)\ior*
\io1 A̠kikiom egunuguma̠ \ior (5:7-20)\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Ibheleguma̠
\p 
\v 1 Ami̠ A̠zemsi̠ ob̠a̠ra̠motu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st na̠ age̠ na̠ a̠ruom inyin ra̠ d̠iobh na̠ i̠wal (12) roghol ya̠ na̠ e̠sasaragi̠an d̠a̠ rebhugh e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠. Ami̠ na̠ a̠bheleguma̠ inyin.
\s1 Ro̠d̠aokpon na̠ Rad̠agi̠an
\p 
\v 2 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, ibhone ma̠ ologi ma̠ igiel a̠d̠ien kere kere ro̠d̠aokpon na̠ e̠te̠i̠ inyin.
\v 3 Iloghome ma̠a̠, ro̠d̠aokpon i̠ye̠ na̠ e̠d̠a ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin na̠ ekpon, sa̠ na̠ ed̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ orue one ma̠ a̠ma̠ne.
\v 4 Ya̠a̠, iwia̠ne ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ one kabar kabar obhin ka̠ okunugiom, b̠o̠ka̠ inyin od̠ikighu ma̠ aru̠mu̠, o̠ghu̠a oleghemeni, sa̠ abar ko o̠kparama d̠o̠ inyin.
\v 5 Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ na̠ ebhir o̠ni̠ inyin o̠te̠i̠ eloghomabar, bha̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠puru ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠bhin onyen ologi na̠ a̠nigha̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na. A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ o̠gam d̠o̠ a̠nigha ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠puru i̠na ma̠ abar.
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, ogiel ola̠ anwa na̠ a̠puru ma̠ abar, bhine d̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ma̠ a̠puru. Ologi d̠oyom o̠gba d̠o̠ i̠wal i̠wal, ezin bho̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ ologi na̠ agba i̠wal i̠wal od̠i ka̠ opoka̠na̠n amu̠m d̠a̠ abadi̠ wa̠ okukugh na̠ a̠pughe na̠ a̠nuom na̠ agi̠, na̠ a̠nuom a̠ru bho̠.
\v 7 O̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a o̠ru̠ru̠an d̠o̠ ma̠a̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rue ate̠i̠ abar d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠.
\v 8 O̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a, bha̠ ologi na̠ agba i̠wal i̠wal, sa̠ na̠ a̠kpokolo d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar d̠o̠yo̠.
\s1 Igoiny na̠ E̠li̠la
\p 
\v 9 Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ onin id̠umom ta̠ Akrai̠st, ola̠ a̠goiny d̠a̠ e̠kal abar, bha̠ a̠bhon ologi ma̠ igiel A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠b̠eton i̠na.
\v 10 Ya̠a̠, o̠li̠la o̠ni̠ ola̠ od̠i d̠a̠ onin id̠umom ta̠ Akrai̠st, a̠bhon ologi ma̠ igiel A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠guri i̠na d̠a̠ a̠dila̠de o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu. Ezin bho̠, o̠li̠la o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠ru sa̠ ta̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ra̠lele i̠gho̠gho̠ ologi ed̠um na̠ e̠nyu̠n na̠ emugughu bho̠.
\v 11 Ra̠lele bho̠ na̠ e̠nyu̠n d̠a̠ ebula̠ e̠si̠so̠ ogogo bho̠. Obom e̠si̠so̠ bho̠ na̠ api̠e̠ ma̠ i̠mu̠nu̠mu̠n na̠ a̠libhon ra̠lele bho̠. Obha̠ onin agu̠o̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar o̠li̠la bho̠ ta̠ eten emunia̠n.
\v 12 Itutumeni ta̠ e̠ro̠ enigha̠ ma̠ i̠na o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠ne amara gigiribh d̠a̠ ad̠agi̠an bho̠, ezin bho̠ ta̠ ozuom i̠na ma̠ eghoiy a̠ghud̠um wa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠gua̠n onigha̠ ogbo ya̠ itula̠n i̠na bho̠.
\v 13 O̠ni̠ ola̠ ad̠agi̠an i̠te̠i̠ o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠a̠, “A̠zib̠a na̠ ad̠agi̠an ami̠.” Ezin bho̠, ko orue d̠o̠ o̠d̠agi̠an A̠zib̠a ma̠ ogir i̠karabh, sa̠ i̠na na̠ agu̠o̠ eka̠ o̠d̠agi̠an d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ nyen.
\v 14 Ya̠a̠, i̠karabh ebhiroma̠ o̠ni̠ na̠ agu̠o̠, na̠ e̠le̠ge̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠, na̠ e̠nyagh o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ ed̠ighom d̠a̠ i̠karabh.
\v 15 Sa̠, igiel o̠ni̠ a̠guri ma̠ i̠karabh ebhiroma̠ d̠a̠ ologi, sa̠ na̠ e̠mar i̠karabh na̠ emutiom, sa̠ igiel i̠karabh bho̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠, sa̠ na̠ eruom omugh.
\v 16 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ ed̠ighologi d̠ami̠, o̠ni̠ ogelemeni d̠o̠ inyin.
\v 17 Kerekere ob̠eb̠i abar na̠ ob̠eb̠i e̠ne̠ghe̠ na̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny na̠ a̠ru, d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ O̠we̠de̠ wa̠ ale̠m re̠b̠alab̠al ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ e̠nai̠ny bho̠. I̠na na̠ onwegia̠n d̠o̠, i̠na na̠ od̠ura̠n d̠o̠ a̠mutiom okokogh azi̠m nyen.
\v 18 D̠a̠ i̠to̠ d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠bhin o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nwe amar i̠yar, a̠tenemeni ma̠ i̠pu̠r imuma̠ d̠a̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na ale̠m bho̠.
\s1 O̠nagha o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ // na̠ ogir iya̠ na̠ agba bho̠
\p 
\v 19 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ ed̠ighologi d̠ami̠, i̠mu̠gho̠nyane̠ ma̠a̠: a̠bhon ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ma̠ obhin d̠a̠ onyen o̠nagha abar, na̠ okimeni ozu kisa̠ ofugh abar. I̠na o̠nu̠r d̠o̠ agam i̠gam,
\v 20 ezin bho̠ i̠gam o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ko orue d̠o̠ emutiom a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠ ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh o̠bi̠gh bho̠.
\v 21 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠we̠le̠mane̠ kerekere ado̠l i̠b̠i̠si̠ghe̠ni̠an na̠ i̠karabh ya̠ na̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ omite omite bho̠. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠, i̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu ma̠ e̠da ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ wa̠ i̠na a̠gbebh d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin bho̠, wa̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠tenemeni inyin bho̠.
\v 22 O̠ni̠ ko o̠gaga ma̠ e̠nagha ma̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ bho̠ ku̠ku̠m, ma̠ egelemeni ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin, ya̠a̠ igire ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ bho̠ na̠ agba bho̠.
\v 23 O̠ni̠ ola̠ amu̠gho̠n o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ bho̠, sa̠ awe̠le̠man ogir agu̠o̠ agba bho̠, bha̠ agu̠b̠an o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bha̠gha̠ ma̠ a̠misigh d̠o̠yo̠ d̠a̠ obha̠gha̠ma̠,
\v 24 sa̠ a̠ten ad̠u̠a, sa̠ a̠weleta̠n agu̠o̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ od̠i, ma̠ i̠se̠ onin obhel bho̠.
\v 25 Ya̠a̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ amar a̠kimeni a̠kpon eb̠la̠ oloko wa̠ na̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ a̠nwunom bho̠, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ ogir ogir o̠ku̠a, sa̠ oweleta̠n d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na amu̠gho̠n bho̠, bha̠ A̠zib̠a ta̠ a̠tutumeni ma̠ ogir o̠ni̠ bho̠.
\v 26 O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ aru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠ i̠na na̠ a̠loghom A̠zib̠a̠, ya̠a̠ na̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ osibhom a̠nem d̠o̠yo̠, bha̠ na̠ a̠gelemeni ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠, sa̠ ologhom A̠zib̠a̠ d̠o̠yo̠ aro̠ ma̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠.
\v 27 Ologhom A̠zib̠a̠ d̠a̠ a̠gi̠a̠ga̠i̠ sa̠ abar o̠li̠o̠m o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠, bha̠ o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ onigha̠ anwi̠i̠ny ya̠ onweni na̠ o̠we̠de̠ o̠to̠, na̠ rekpukele anwani̠ d̠a̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu d̠awa, na̠ oghel i̠karabh ado̠l e̠mara̠nwunom.
\c 2
\s1 Ko okpon a̠misigh a̠gir abar
\p 
\v 1 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, ogbo ya̠ ima̠ra̠ ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st wa̠ isosorogia̠n bho̠, o̠ni̠ ko okpon o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ma̠ egir abar.
\v 2 Obhin o̠tu̠o̠m ma̠a̠, odi o̠li̠la o̠ni̠ ola̠ alo̠gi̠an ra̠gulu a̠gol sa̠ a̠bhin ib̠ebi̠ a̠rukpe a̠bura̠, na̠ onyigoiny o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠bhin igba̠iny ipupu a̠rukpe a̠bura̠, ed̠igh eru d̠a̠ esi a̠kokod̠ia̠n d̠inyin.
\v 3 Ka̠ inyin ubhin o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠bura̠ ma̠ ib̠eb̠i ibura̠ bho̠ i̠tu̠o̠m abar upu, sa̠ inyin u̠gba inigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ ob̠eb̠i esi onon,” sa̠ inyin u̠gba unigha̠ ma̠ onyigoiny bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Mara ma̠ i̠se̠,” bo̠d̠o̠ “Ro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ a̠de d̠a̠ aka i̠kasi̠ o̠gbam a̠wel d̠ami̠.”
\v 4 O̠ku̠a sa̠ na̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠, inyin na̠ o̠bhe̠l odi na̠ okpon odi na̠ ogurumeni d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin, sa̠ inyin na̠ oten ogbo osobh ase̠ i̠karabh i̠walama.
\v 5 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, i̠mare̠ ma̠ e̠nagha. A̠zib̠a̠ aso̠n inyigoiny a̠nwunom e̠mara̠nwunom bho̠ ma̠ onwuna̠ ibom ologi ima̠ra̠, na̠ od̠igh na̠ o̠yo̠ od̠ed̠ia̠n d̠a̠ irileghom d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠gua̠n a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ itula̠n i̠na bho̠.
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, inyin na̠ okpon ronyigoiny bho̠ na̠ ogurumeni. Aru̠lala bho̠ d̠o̠ ke̠re̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ eponoma̠ inyin bho̠? Awa d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ed̠ud̠ur inyin na̠ ka̠ ed̠ighom d̠a̠ a̠rutu ase̠ bho̠ ke̠re̠?
\v 7 Awa d̠o̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ efugh i̠basi̠ na̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ ob̠eb̠i a̠d̠ien wa̠ na̠ oseniom inyin bho̠ d̠o̠ ke̠re̠?
\v 8 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠, inyin na̠ okoko ma̠ oloko wa̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, wa̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Tula̠ne ma̠ o̠ni̠ etua̠n d̠oyom ma̠ agu̠o̠ anwa itula̠n ozu d̠oyom bho̠,” bha̠ inyin na̠ o̠mar na̠ ogir.
\v 9 Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠, inyin okpon a̠nwunom d̠a̠ a̠misigh ogir abar, bha̠ inyin u̠mar d̠o̠ ogir, sa̠ oloko bho̠ ta̠ a̠sobh ase̠ a̠bhumeni inyin ma̠a̠ inyin id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh.
\v 10 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ a̠koko ma̠ eb̠la̠ roloko bho̠ sa̠ a̠sor odi, bha̠ i̠na a̠sor eb̠la̠yi.
\v 11 Onin A̠zib̠a̠ wa̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Ko od̠e ma̠ e̠ma” bho̠, agba ma̠a̠, “Ko ogigh o̠ni̠.” Ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ anwa od̠e d̠o̠ ma̠ e̠ma, sa̠ anwa igigh o̠ni̠, bha̠ anwa na̠ a̠ten o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠sor oloko bho̠.
\v 12 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, a̠fugh o̠nu̠ d̠inyin, na̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar d̠inyin, e̠ro̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ita̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ ta̠ obhin oloko wa̠ a̠tenemeni i̠yar bho̠ osobh ase̠ ogboloma̠.
\v 13 Igire ma̠ o̠ku̠a, ezin bho̠, d̠a̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠, ko okpon d̠o̠ ma̠ igbirigbir ogboloma̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ okpon d̠o̠ ma̠ ipa̠n ogbo ma̠ igbirigbir. Igbirigbir na̠ ane̠gi̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ osobh ase̠.
\s1 Ologi Ima̠ra̠ na̠ ogir
\p 
\v 14 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ agba ma̠a̠ i̠na a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠, ya̠a̠ i̠na na̠ obhin d̠o̠ a̠gir abar, ka̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ola̠ o̠ku̠a ta̠ a̠rue a̠tenemeni i̠na ke̠re̠?
\v 15 Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ inyin ologhom umor, bo̠d̠o̠ u̠marani̠ ola̠ onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠ga̠i akapa, bo̠d̠o̠ ed̠ia̠n ya̠ od̠e,
\v 16 sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ inyin agba a̠nigha̠ i̠na ma̠a̠, “Gi̠e̠ na̠ ekima̠! Okirika̠ od̠ighi d̠o̠ nya̠m, ma̠ ate̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n ya̠ od̠e olegha̠n!” Ya̠a̠, anwa na̠ onigha̠ d̠o̠ i̠na ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ a̠puru bho̠, ka̠ asu̠o̠ bho̠ ka̠ ere?
\v 17 Onin agu̠o̠ bho̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ola̠ ogir o̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠o̠ aro̠ ma̠ omumugh.
\v 18 Obhin o̠tu̠o̠m ma̠a̠ odi o̠ni̠ agba ma̠a̠, “Anwa a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠, ya̠a̠ ami̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ ogir.” Sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ awo̠ran ma̠a̠, “Leriome ami̠ ma̠a̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠oyom ya̠ ogir o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ bho̠, sa̠ ami̠ ta̠ a̠bhin rogir d̠ami̠ a̠leriom anwa ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠ami̠.”
\v 19 Anwa a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠a̠ onin A̠zib̠a̠ od̠i. A̠bhon o̠ku̠a. A̠ruru bho̠ eka̠ ema̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ na̠ eghil a̠rugugu na̠ ebhin igiri.
\v 20 Anwa ema̠ o̠ni̠! Anwa na̠ abho̠ro̠gh o̠bi̠gh elegh ola̠ ta̠ a̠leriom ma̠a̠, ologi ima̠ra̠ ogir o̠to̠ ma̠ obhobho i̠kpo̠, d̠u̠ko̠?
\v 21 Obom o̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar Ebraham, sa̠ A̠zib̠a̠ a̠bhelegi ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ igielake̠ d̠a̠ ebula̠ ogir wa̠ a̠gir igiel bho̠ i̠na agbam o̠nyi̠ d̠o̠yo̠ Azi̠ki̠ d̠a̠ enwen i̠ko̠l bho̠.
\v 22 Anwa na̠ abi̠gh agu̠o̠ i̠na a̠tulugi ma̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠yo̠ na̠ rogir d̠o̠yo̠. Sa̠ ubhin rogir d̠o̠yo̠ umuzoghod̠iom ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠yo̠.
\v 23 Onon a̠muzoghod̠iom agu̠o̠ u̠gba d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, “Ebraham a̠ma̠ra̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠ye̠ iten od̠ighi i̠d̠iar igielake̠\x - \xo 2:23 \xt Ob̠et 15:6\x* ya̠ u̠lo̠gho̠m unigha̠ i̠na.” Sa̠ ubhelegi i̠na ma̠ a̠tologha̠n\x - \xo 2:23 \xt Azaya 41:8\x* ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 24 I̠se̠n, inyin na̠ o̠bi̠gh ma̠a̠ ogir ya̠ a̠nwunom na̠ egir na̠ eguri awa ma̠ a̠dila̠de e̠b̠ab̠ala d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠awa ku̠ku̠m d̠o̠.
\v 25 Obha̠ onin agu̠o̠ ubhin u̠bi̠gh A̠rehab od̠eme̠ma bho̠ ma̠ ani̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala, d̠a̠ ebula̠ ogir ya̠ i̠na a̠gir igiel bho̠ i̠na ada ma̠ ogbo ipoiny bho̠ a̠bhin, sa̠ a̠ruom awa ma̠ o̠wo̠l opa̠n agba o̠d̠u̠a bho̠.
\v 26 Agu̠o̠ ozu o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ola̠ ipoghu o̠to̠ aro̠ ma̠ omumugh bho̠, obha̠ onin agu̠o̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ ola̠ ogir o̠to̠ aro̠ ma̠ omumugh.
\c 3
\s1 Osibhom A̠nem
\p 
\v 1 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, o̠ni̠ ko owia̠n agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠d̠izo inyin ta̠ oten ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠. Ezin bho̠, inyin ologhom ma̠a̠ osobh ase̠ d̠i̠yar ogbo atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ bho̠ i̠kpar epu.
\v 2 Eb̠la̠ i̠yar, o̠ni̠ ola̠ o̠pi̠o̠mghan d̠o̠ ma̠ abar d̠a̠ a̠d̠izo re̠kal bo̠. Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ o̠ni̠ ta̠ a̠rue a̠sibhom a̠nem d̠o̠yo̠ ma̠ ola̠ ko ofugh d̠o̠ ma̠ abar api̠e̠, bha̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠legha̠n d̠a̠ a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠rue a̠sibhom eb̠la̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠.
\v 3 I̠yar na̠ o̠kpu̠o̠m rikoli d̠a̠ aru̠nu̠ ro̠su̠ bo̠ka̠ i̠yar orue orileghom awa obhin o̠gi̠ kesikesi ola̠ a̠d̠igh i̠yar ologi.
\v 4 Bo̠d̠o̠, ikpone ma̠ agu̠o̠ a̠rughugh abadi̠ i̠bu̠gh i̠te̠i̠, na̠ agu̠o̠ i̠kparakpar rogim na̠ egim na̠ eb̠oroghom, ku̠ku̠m eka̠, na̠ obhin o̠nyi̠ o̠gbara o̠d̠o̠m na̠ ob̠or, sa̠ na̠ agi̠ ma̠ agba o̠la ibhir i̠yar ob̠or o̠gi̠o̠m.
\v 5 Onin agu̠o̠ a̠nem od̠i. D̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ali̠ki̠r d̠o̠yo̠ eka̠, na̠ are̠ma ma̠ ibom i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠rue a̠gir. Obha̠ agu̠o̠ o̠gbara eb̠olob̠ol anya ta̠ a̠rue a̠mumor anu̠o̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ obom e̠ghana.
\v 6 A̠nem od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ anya. A̠nem o̠karabh a̠limon ola̠ na̠ api̠e̠gi̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠risisi ozu o̠ni̠, sa̠ na̠ ata ma̠ anya ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠ghud̠um o̠ni̠, sa̠ i̠na na̠ agu̠o̠ eka̠ na̠ a̠mumor na̠ anya ya̠ e̠banya ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠ bho̠ ata i̠na.
\v 7 O̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ i̠nam ologi ed̠um, a̠d̠igh i̠di̠ar ya̠ na̠ e̠bhe̠bhe̠ghu̠, a̠d̠igh i̠nam ya̠ na̠ ekpulughu, na̠ i̠nam abadi̠, na̠ ina̠, sa̠ na̠ a̠rue na̠ a̠kponom awa.
\v 8 Ya̠a̠, o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ta̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ osibhom a̠nem d̠o̠yo̠. I̠karabh ya̠ enen na̠ ebha̠, na̠ i̠d̠ai̠ iya̠ na̠ eruom omugh, imuzo d̠a̠ a̠nem o̠ni̠.
\v 9 I̠yar na̠ obhin a̠nem na̠ otutumeni ma̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ na̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar, sa̠ na̠ obhin onin a̠nem bho̠ na̠ orogi ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ale̠m agu̠b̠e̠ni̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠
\v 10 I̠yar na̠ obhin onin o̠nu̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠mutioghom itutumeni na̠ itogi. A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, na̠ obhon d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ o̠ku̠a.
\v 11 Amu̠m a̠b̠ugu na̠ amu̠m ala ta̠ erue emite d̠a̠ onin ogugua̠ amu̠m ke̠re̠?
\v 12 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, oriren a̠fig ta̠ a̠rue a̠mum itu oliv ke̠re̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠ od̠id̠igh a̠grep ta̠ a̠rue a̠mum itu a̠fig ke̠re̠? Amu̠m a̠b̠ugu ta̠ erue emite d̠a̠ ogugua̠ amu̠m ola̠ amu̠m ala imuzo ke̠re̠?
\s1 I̠wal A̠d̠ien Eloghom Abar
\p 
\v 13 Ogbo ya̠ iloghom abar sa̠ inwuna̠ ma̠ amu̠gho̠nyan od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin ke̠re̠? Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ od̠i, bha̠ awa ebhin d̠a̠ a̠ma̠rugh igielake̠, na̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu, na̠ eloghom abar d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ i̠di̠ar, eleriom o̠ku̠a.
\v 14 Ya̠a̠, ku̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠kparakpar a̠gbokia̠n na̠ o̠ku̠ku̠ imuzo d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin, bha̠ o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ obhin obo, bo̠d̠o̠ ta̠ o̠gba ma̠ igunugha̠ okpegiom a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠.
\v 15 Eloghom abar ya̠ o̠ku̠a i̠d̠u̠a d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny eru, ya̠a̠, i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom eru, sa̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ iya̠ Eru bho̠.
\v 16 Esi ola̠ a̠gbokia̠n na̠ o̠ku̠ku̠ od̠i, i̠se̠ esi asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an na̠ a̠d̠ien kerekere i̠karabh od̠i nyen.
\v 17 Ya̠a̠, eloghom abar ola̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠ru, bha̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ia̠ aro̠ ma̠ abar ola̠ e̠b̠ab̠ala, sa̠ ta̠ a̠mutiom ekima̠, na̠ o̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ozu, na̠ etula̠n. Ta̠ a̠muzo na̠ okpon igbirigbir, sa̠ ta̠ a̠mum imuma̠ ib̠eb̠i od̠ighi i̠di̠ar, ko o̠bhe̠l d̠o̠ ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ a̠kpon opa̠n a̠gurumeni, sa̠ ko o̠gba d̠o̠ ma̠ opa̠n abar a̠gir opa̠n nyen.
\v 18 A̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ ed̠ighi ma̠ ekima̠ na̠ egbebh ikpo ekima̠, sa̠ ta̠ eb̠u ma̠ ikpo ed̠ia̠n igielake̠.
\c 4
\s1 Inigha̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin A̠zib̠a̠
\p 
\v 1 Eb̠la̠ relobhiri na̠ ro̠b̠e̠m d̠inyin ka̠ na̠ e̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠ken na̠ eru? Awa i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ ebhiroma̠ e̠me̠me̠m i̠di̠ar e̠mara̠nwunom, ya̠ na̠ ewia̠n inyin kigiel kigiel d̠a̠ rologi d̠inyin bho̠ eru, ke̠re̠?
\v 2 Inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh o̠te̠i̠ i̠di̠ar, ya̠a̠, inyin urue d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠te̠i̠, sa̠ inyin na̠ o̠ze̠gi̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom. Inyin na̠ o̠si̠matan i̠d̠i̠ar, ya̠a̠ inyin u̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠, sa̠ inyin na̠ o̠bu̠man na̠ owe. Inyin u̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ inyin na̠ o̠bho̠ro̠gh bho̠, ezin bho̠ inyin upuru d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 3 Ya̠a̠, igiel inyin upuru, inyin u̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠, ezin bho̠ inyin upuru ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ osora̠n d̠o̠. Inyin na̠ opuru ma̠ o̠te̠i̠ i̠di̠ar e̠me̠me̠m e̠mara̠nwunom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin.
\v 4 Inyin rod̠eme̠ma! Inyin uloghom d̠o̠ ma̠a̠, od̠igh na̠ e̠mara̠nwunom orilogha̠n na̠ a̠tenemeni inyin ogbo o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ke̠re̠? O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ola̠ aso̠n otula̠n e̠mara̠nwunom na̠ a̠ten o̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠.
\v 5 Bo̠d̠o̠ ka̠, inyin na̠ o̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠, abar wa̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ agba ma̠a̠, “E̠mu̠gh d̠o̠yo̠ wa̠ i̠na alo̠gh a̠guri d̠a̠ rologi d̠i̠yar bho̠, a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ obom etula̠n ya̠ a̠gbokia̠n a̠gboloma̠ i̠yar, sa̠ na̠ abho̠ro̠gh i̠yar o̠ro̠ iyo̠yo̠ ku̠ku̠m,” ma̠ ezin bo̠ ke̠re̠?
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ ane̠ghe̠ ma̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ya̠ i̠bu̠gh ipu ma̠ o̠ku̠a. Obha̠ ezin bho̠ u̠gba d̠a̠ A̠d̠ire E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠,
\q1 “A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ adamaghan ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu bho̠,
\q2 sa̠ na̠ abhe̠l ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu bho̠.”\x - \xo 4:6 \xt Ra̠sid 3:34\x*
\p 
\v 7 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, i̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin ma̠ enigha̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a. I̠damaghane̠ ma̠ Eru bho̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠kpo ma̠ eghil awe̠le̠ inyin ad̠u̠a.
\v 8 Itua̠ne ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠tua̠n inyin. I̠titola̠ ma̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠inyin, inyin rod̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh! I̠b̠ab̠alame̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi d̠inyin, inyin ibhelebhel!
\v 9 I̠ku̠nu̠, ileghe, ma̠ e̠gba ma̠ igbir, ma̠ etenemeni ma̠ adi̠e̠l d̠inyin ed̠i, ado̠l o̠d̠e̠ d̠inyin eten i̠ku̠nu̠.
\v 10 I̠ki̠ri̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠b̠eton inyin.
\s1 A̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ // O̠bi̠gh ipa̠n ogbo o̠pi̠e̠
\p 
\v 11 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, odi ofugh d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠karabh a̠fugh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ odi. Ku̠gba ma̠a̠, o̠ni̠ a̠fugh i̠karabh a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ a̠sobh ase̠ a̠gboloma̠ awa, bha̠ i̠na abi̠gh Oloko bho̠ api̠e̠, sa̠ a̠sobh ase̠ a̠gboloma̠. Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ inyin osobh ase̠ ogboloma̠ ma̠ Oloko bho̠, bha̠ inyin ukoko d̠o̠ ma̠ Oloko bho̠, ya̠a̠ inyin na̠ oten ogbo osobh ase̠.
\v 12 A̠zib̠a̠ ku̠ku̠m a̠nigha̠ ma̠ Oloko bho̠, sa̠ aro̠ ma̠ osobh ma̠ ase̠ bho̠. I̠na ku̠ku̠m a̠nwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon otenemeni na̠ o̠pi̠e̠gi̠. O̠ku̠a ka̠ anwa inwuna̠ ma̠ a̠kere a̠limon osobh ase̠ onigha̠ o̠ni̠ etua̠n d̠oyom?
\s1 Ighubha̠ ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ elegien a̠ru
\p 
\v 13 I̠se̠n i̠nagha, inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠, “A̠didon bo̠d̠o̠ elegien a̠ru, i̠yar ta̠ o̠gi̠ d̠a̠ e̠ma onon bo̠d̠o̠ e̠ma obha̠, ka̠ o̠ro̠ ma̠ e̠mu̠ ala, ob̠ua̠ ma̠ a̠b̠ua̠ o̠te̠i̠ asu̠o̠.”
\v 14 Ya̠a̠, inyin ologhom agu̠o̠ ra̠ghud̠um d̠inyin ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ elegien a̠ru, ke̠re̠? Inyin od̠i ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠bhu̠bhu̠lu̠gi̠ ya̠ imite i̠ro̠ ma̠ ekud̠i obhel, a̠tepa̠ sa̠ iten obhobho i̠kpo̠ i̠mai̠ny i̠d̠u̠a nyen.
\v 15 Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ inyin ta̠ o̠gba kuma̠ o̠ko̠no̠n, “Ku̠gba ma̠a̠ od̠i d̠a̠ i̠to̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠, bha̠ na̠ ebhir i̠yar o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ a̠ghud̠um ogir abar onon, bo̠d̠o̠, abar obha̠.”
\v 16 Ya̠a̠, i̠se̠n bha̠ inyin na̠ o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu, na̠ okue na̠ otutuma̠. Eb̠la̠ o̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ a̠ruzu i̠ye̠ i̠karabh.
\v 17 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, o̠ni̠ ola̠ a̠loghom ib̠eb̠i ya̠ i̠kpe̠ i̠na ma̠ ogir, sa̠ awe̠le̠ ma̠ ogir, bha̠ i̠na na̠ a̠gir i̠karabh.
\c 5
\s1 I̠kparakpar Ikikiom ya̠ Igboloma̠ ma̠ Aru̠lala
\p 
\v 1 Inyin aru̠lala bho̠ i̠nagha ami̠! Ileghe ma̠ e̠gba ma̠ igbir ma̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ e̠kparama ado̠l wa̠ na̠ a̠ru ra̠ o̠te̠i̠ inyin bho̠.
\v 2 E̠li̠la d̠inyin na̠ e̠b̠o̠ro̠ghu̠ ebhe, sa̠ ad̠u̠i̠ny na̠ ed̠e ma̠ a̠rukpe d̠inyin e̠pi̠e̠.
\v 3 A̠gol na̠ a̠silva̠ d̠inyin na̠ ed̠ikighu ma̠ o̠sari̠, sa̠ o̠sari̠ bho̠ ta̠ e̠ro̠ ma̠ elegh ebhum ase̠ d̠inyin, sa̠ o̠sari̠ bho̠ ta̠ ed̠e ma̠ ipulupul ozu d̠inyin agu̠o̠ anya. Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, inyin od̠id̠ia̠ na̠ okpol e̠li̠la d̠a̠ ra̠d̠a̠ma̠ ekunuguma̠ i̠nye̠n.
\v 4 Bi̠ghe̠! Anwa ta̠ o̠kpe̠gi̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ikpoki ogbo ya̠ anwa i̠ko̠ ma̠ ogir onigha̠ oyom d̠a̠ ari̠si̠ d̠oyom bho̠, sa̠ i̠se̠n sa̠ ikpoki ya̠ anwa ta̠ o̠kpe̠gi̠ d̠o̠ awa bho̠ na̠ eleghe na̠ emulughu ma̠a̠ olo aro̠ a̠nigha̠ nyam. I̠nagha, Wa̠nwuna̠ ma̠ eb̠la̠ a̠limon bho̠ na̠ amu̠gho̠n red̠i ogbo ob̠u ed̠ia̠n d̠oyom bho̠.
\v 5 I̠se̠n d̠a̠ e̠mara̠nwunom, inyin na̠ orugh ado̠l od̠e e̠li̠la odudugina̠, na̠ ogir i̠di̠ar ya̠ obhonomeni rologi d̠inyin. Inyin na̠ ob̠ologh ekpo na̠ ob̠a̠ra̠ ma̠ a̠d̠a̠ma̠ wa̠ ta̠ o̠ze̠ inyin o̠kanyo̠gh bho̠.
\v 6 Inyin na̠ osobh ase̠ obhumeni ma̠ a̠nwunom, na̠ o̠ze̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠pi̠o̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ abar, ya̠ orue d̠o̠ ma̠ owia̠n inyin bho̠.
\s1 A̠ma̠ne na̠ A̠siseiny
\p 
\v 7 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, ine ma̠ eb̠a̠ra̠ ma̠ obhel Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru. I̠bi̠ghe̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogbebh ma̠ ed̠ia̠n aro̠ na̠ a̠b̠a̠ra̠ ma̠ obhel ikpo ya̠ i̠na a̠gbebh bho̠ ta̠ eb̠om ed̠ia̠n ya̠ ilei abar. I̠na na̠ a̠ne na̠ a̠b̠a̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠lo̠bha wa̠ ta̠ a̠b̠on alo̠bh bho̠, na̠ o̠lo̠bha wa̠ ta̠ alo̠bh o̠gu̠man bho̠.
\v 8 Inyin eka̠, ine ma̠ eb̠a̠ra̠. O̠ni̠ ko odugh, eb̠em ologi d̠inyin abu̠gh, ezin bho̠ eruoma̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ ate̠i̠ d̠a̠ e̠b̠ab̠a agu̠o̠.
\v 9 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, odi oghunuma̠ d̠o̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ odi, bo̠ka̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ osobh ase̠ a̠bhumeni inyin. O̠ni̠ osobh ase̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠loghom amara d̠a̠ o̠nu̠otu bho̠.
\v 10 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, i̠ta ma̠ ado̠l a̠ma̠ne ta̠ a̠riwil ya̠ ibhin a̠d̠ien ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ i̠gba ma̠ asu̠gbagba bho̠. Awa ine ma̠ a̠ma̠ne d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ali̠gam a̠ruzu ya̠ i̠te̠i̠ awa bho̠.
\v 11 I̠nagha! I̠yar na̠ obhin ma̠a̠ na̠ otutumeni ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ine ma̠ a̠ma̠ne d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io ali̠gam a̠ruzu bho̠. Inyin na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n ogboloma̠ ma̠ a̠ma̠ne ta̠ A̠zobu, sa̠ inyin uloghom agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠na d̠a̠ ekunuguma̠ bho̠. Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠muzo na̠ okpon igbirigbir, obha̠ ezin bho̠ i̠na a̠gir o̠ku̠a bho̠.
\v 12 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ d̠ami̠, wa̠ a̠lei abar a̠pu bho̠, o̠ni̠ ko osibhigha̠ ma̠ ebhin a̠de bho̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ote̠nai̠ny, bo̠d̠o̠ opa̠n abar ed̠ia̠n i̠zo̠. Eb̠la̠ abar wa̠ inyin ta̠ ofugh bho̠, bha̠, “Yii” bo̠d̠o̠, “E̠e̠nyi̠” b̠o̠ka̠ usobh ase̠ obhumeni inyin.
\s1 A̠siseiny Ologi Ima̠ra̠
\p 
\v 13 O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ abi̠gh ali̠gam a̠ruzu d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin od̠i ke̠re̠? I̠na a̠siseiny. O̠ni̠ inyin od̠i d̠a̠ ibo ke̠re̠? I̠na amo̠r aso̠r itutumeni.
\v 14 O̠ni̠ ola̠ na̠ anwe̠r od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin ke̠re̠? I̠na a̠lebh ikei aso̠si̠ bho̠ eru ra̠ esiseiny enigha̠ i̠na, ebhin amu̠nu̠ esigh i̠na, d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠.
\v 15 A̠siseiny ola̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ na̠ a̠lol na̠ a̠koko ma̠ o̠ni̠ asu̠nwe̠r na̠ a̠d̠umeni, sa̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠b̠eton i̠na. Ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠gir i̠karabh eka̠, sa̠ na̠ o̠we̠le̠man i̠karabh bho̠.
\v 16 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, odi agba ma̠ i̠karabh d̠o̠yo̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi, odi a̠siseiny a̠nigha̠ ma̠ odi, bo̠ka̠ awa ed̠um. I̠kparapkar a̠siseiny ta̠ o̠ni̠ igielake̠ enwuna̠ ma̠ a̠limon, sa̠ na̠ elol ibom.
\v 17 I̠lai̠za aro̠ ma̠ o̠nyi̠o̠mo̠ro̠ni̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ i̠yar od̠i bho̠, sa̠ i̠na a̠siseiny agu̠o̠ ola̠ a̠d̠io ko o̠lo̠bh d̠o̠, sa̠ a̠mite ma̠ ola̠ a̠d̠io o̠lo̠bh d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠de bho̠ i̠sar ala na̠ odin uwetire.
\v 18 Sa̠ i̠na a̠mula̠ a̠siseiny, sa̠ e̠nai̠ny bho̠ a̠soroni ma̠ o̠lo̠bha sa̠ a̠de bho̠ a̠b̠om ed̠ia̠n.
\v 19 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, ku̠gba ma̠ odi o̠ni̠ d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin a̠mel ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠, sa̠ odi o̠ni̠ a̠rileghom i̠na a̠mulumeni,
\v 20 bha̠ o̠ni̠ bho̠ a̠loghom ma̠a̠: o̠ni̠ wa̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh a̠tiba̠ra̠ d̠a̠ i̠karabh d̠o̠yo̠ bho̠ a̠tenemeni ma̠ eloghoma̠n ozu ta̠ od̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh bho̠ d̠a̠ omugh, sa̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ na̠ okpon a̠d̠izo i̠karabh na̠ o̠si̠ghe̠ ma̠ a̠d̠ien.
